Great Song The Rap Version Nicki Minaj Made Is So Much Better Than The Original One Aqua Made Is Boring.
Due to Aqua's "Barbie Girl" literally taking over the airwaves two and a half decades ago, I feel fairly confident in saying that this #BarbieWorld song is probably far more "special" to those of us who grew up in the nineties than it is to younger generations.  Like a lot of folks back then, I really tried to hate it and totally failed. And, even at 38, I still get low-key excited anytime I hear the intro:  "Hiya, Barbie!" "Hi, Ken!" "You want to go for a ride?" "Sure, Ken!" "Jump in!"  And yeah, I'm ashamed AF that I've still got it memorized. ğŸ˜‚
